  "texts": [
    "In stage 3 (Fig. 3a; stage 3; post-exposure), participants repeated the task from stage 1.",
    "The primary measure of interest was the change in participants' judgements.",
    "The data were analysed using a mixed model multinomial logistic regression with exposure (before versus after exposure to AI images) as a fixed factor, with random intercepts and slopes at the participant level.",
    "This model was chosen because the dependent variable involved a choice from six distinct and unordered categories (see Supplementary Results for an alternative analysis).",
    "The findings revealed a significant effect for exposure (F(5, 62) = 5.89; P < 0.001; Fig. 3b), indicating that exposure to the AI images altered human judgements."
  ],
